text: The 2001 Nottinghamshire County Council election was held on Thursday, 7 June 2001. The whole council was up for election and the result was the Labour Party retaining its control of the council. ==Election result== |} ==References== 2001 Category:2001 English local elections Category:2000s in Nottinghamshire Category:June 2001 events in the United Kingdom
title: 2001 Nottinghamshire County Council election
